 The two destrons finished the autoguns. Datatron and his comrades walked up 
to them. "Magmatron has arrived. This ship is amazing it picked up his 
signature immediatly. I say we call for an alliance for I doubt he would join 
the council." the other destrons agreed and sent the allie proposal to 
magmatron.
